Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway welcome special guest comedic Youtuber Leon Lush to discuss his viral videos of making fun of public figures who completely deserve it such as Kenneth Copeland, wager who would win in fictional death matches such as Anne Frank vs. Harambe, go through their favorite comedy movies that inspired them and their comedic tastes, and end the show with talking about what is next beyond the Youtube platform for Leon.
